comments.author: BADecker
comments.body: Quote from: Stalker22 on September 13, 2023, 10:20:48 PMQuote from: BADecker on September 13, 2023, 08:50:22 PM~PRES. TRUMP PREDICTED 9/11 19 MONTHS BEFORE IT HAPPENED!So what? The Simpsons predicted this four years before it happened. Heck, The Simpsons even predicted President Trump 16 years before it happened!  Relax man. Don't be so scared. Everybody dies, and when you do, you'll be out of it all... until the Judgment Day, that is.So, live life to its fullest, and enjoy every moment that you can. Your fear is something that is draining you more than anything else.As far as predictions go, if you predict enough stuff, you'll probably get one right once in a while.And, haven't you figured out that the Simpsons are cartoon characters? Their creators might predict stuff, but cartoon characters don't do anything.Please, for your own good, don't watch any scary movies. You might take them to heart, and wake up in a Happy House one morning.
